  user_input {
    user_response: "Create a luxury companion placement website inspired by the emotional and editorial design language of Dior.com.\n\nDo NOT copy Dior.\n\nCapture the feeling of:\n\n- Luxury\n- Exclusivity\n- Heritage\n- Storytelling\n- Craftsmanship\n- Editorial elegance\n\nBrand Name:\nCompanion Couture\n\nIndustry:\nLuxury Companion Placement\n\nTarget Audience:\nAffluent families, professionals, executives, celebrities, and luxury pet owners.\n\nVisual Style:\nMinimalist luxury\nLarge cinematic photography\nEditorial layouts\nWhite space\nChampagne gold accents\nElegant serif typography\nLuxury lifestyle imagery\n\nSite Structure:\nHome\nAvailable Companions\nThe Companion Couture Experience\nAbout\nJournal\nApplication\nContact\n\nPrimary CTA:\nApply For Placement\n\nTone:\nWarm\nSophisticated\nTrustworthy\nExclusive\nEmotional\n\nNever present puppies as products.\n\nPresent each puppy as a carefully curated companion with a story.\n\nEvery page should feel like a luxury fashion brand, private members club, or five-star hospitality experience.\n\nPrioritize storytelling over selling.\n\nDesign for emotional connection first and conversion second. Ensure all typography is refined and whitespace is abundant.\n\n Use sophisticated editorial layouts to showcase each individual dog\'s unique personality and heritage.\n\n Incorporate subtle micro-animations that respond to scroll to evoke a sense of movement.\n\nCompanion Couture = Companionship + Heritage + Exclusivity This should feel like a high-end fashion editorial tailored for canine lovers."
    items {
      text: "Create a luxury companion placement website inspired by the emotional and editorial design language of Dior.com.\n\nDo NOT copy Dior.\n\nCapture the feeling of:\n\n- Luxury\n- Exclusivity\n- Heritage\n- Storytelling\n- Craftsmanship\n- Editorial elegance\n\nBrand Name:\nCompanion Couture\n\nIndustry:\nLuxury Companion Placement\n\nTarget Audience:\nAffluent families, professionals, executives, celebrities, and luxury pet owners.\n\nVisual Style:\nMinimalist luxury\nLarge cinematic photography\nEditorial layouts\nWhite space\nChampagne gold accents\nElegant serif typography\nLuxury lifestyle imagery\n\nSite Structure:\nHome\nAvailable Companions\nThe Companion Couture Experience\nAbout\nJournal\nApplication\nContact\n\nPrimary CTA:\nApply For Placement\n\nTone:\nWarm\nSophisticated\nTrustworthy\nExclusive\nEmotional\n\nNever present puppies as products.\n\nPresent each puppy as a carefully curated companion with a story.\n\nEvery page should feel like a luxury fashion brand, private members club, or five-star hospitality experience.\n\nPrioritize storytelling over selling.\n\nDesign for emotional connection first and conversion second. Ensure all typography is refined and whitespace is abundant.\n\n Use sophisticated editorial layouts to showcase each individual dog\'s unique personality and heritage.\n\n Incorporate subtle micro-animations that respond to scroll to evoke a sense of movement.\n\nCompanion Couture = Companionship + Heritage + Exclusivity This should feel like a high-end fashion editorial tailored for canine lovers."
    }
  }
