  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Concluding the Process**\n\nI\'ve successfully completed the application build, and it\'s running perfectly! Now, I am focused on crafting a polished final response. I\'m reviewing the communication style guidelines to ensure a seamless and appropriate conclusion to this turn.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have completed the single-page luxury companion placement website for **Companion Couture**, inspired by the elegant, emotional, and layout-rich storytelling of modern high-fashion editorials. \n\n### \360\237\216\250 Editorial Identity & Design Philosophy\n- **Cormorant Garamond Pairing**: Set display headings, breed certificates, and heritage narratives in an elegant, thin-weight luxury serif typeface. This is balanced by **Inter** for clean, legible interface text and **JetBrains Mono** to authenticate unique registration numbers, dates, and scores.\n- **Champagne Gold & Slate Accents**: Set the interface on a pristine, airy stone-white canvas featuring gold hairline dividers, luxurious ivory backdrops, and deep charcoal and sable contrast banners to evoke the feeling of a private gallery.\n- **Dignity Over Product**: Removed all references to standard pet-store terminology. Puppies are treated as noble canine companions with direct lineage pedigrees, custom psychological profiles, and emotional narratives rather than simple commodities.\n\n### \360\237\217\233\357\270\217 Structural Modules\n- **The Atelier (Hero & Showcase)**: Features an immersive cinematic hero section detailing early-rearing excellence, a direct preview slider of curated active placements, and highlights from our private gazette.\n- **Available Placements Catalog**: An interactive showcase filterable by gender, breed group, and reservation status. Clicking any companion opens their full **Heritage Dossier** (pedigree, DNA clearance certifications, OFA health reports, and personalized character story).\n- **The Experience (Four Pillars of Excellence)**: Articulates our elite standards across four scroll-staggered pillars: *Hereditary Genome Auditing*, the *Parisian Sensory Nursery*, our *Royal Chauffeur Concierge*, and the *Atelier Welcome Kit*.\n- **The Heritage (About)**: Details our century-old Swiss Alps origin story, alongside private appointments and visitations at our *Geneva Lakeside* and *Palm Beach Coastal* estates.\n- **The Private Gazette (Journal)**: Features full-length, beautifully designed editorial publications exploring early behavioral science, canine ergonomics, and matching alignment.\n- **Private Placement Registry (Application Form)**: A multi-step questionnaire that guides guardians through direct contact details, residency scale alignment, lifestyle integration, and agreement to our strict Ethical Placement Charter.\n- **Liaison Office (Concierge Direct)**: A highly confidential contact center for family office representatives, complete with secure direct dispatch.\n"
    thinking_duration {
      nanos: 644375747
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
